Title: The Gunmen
Description: While traveling through a small Texas town, Little Joe and Hoss are mistaken for the gunslinging Slade Brothers who have been hired to kill a man.
Short Description: Little Joe and Hoss are mistaken for murderous gunslingers.

Title: The Fear Merchants
Description: In Virginia City the Cartwrights protect a young Chinese man who has been accused of murder. A mayor candidate uses the situation to further his cause.
Short Description: The Cartwrights protect a young Chinese man who has been accused of murder.

Title: Death at Dawn
Description: The Cartwrights help the sheriff bring a murderer to trial but are opposed by the murderer’s boss.
Short Description: The Cartwrights help the sheriff bring a murderer to trial but are opposed by the murderer’s boss.

Title: The Spitfire
Description: Little Joe is forced to kill a man who started a fire on the Ponderosa. He takes responsibility for the man’s daughter, unaware inlaws are on the way to exact revenge.
Short Description: Little Joe is forced to kill a man who started a fire on the Ponderosa.

Title: The Blood Line
Description: After killing a man in self-defense, Ben feels he is responsible to look after the man’s son returning from Boston, but he only wants revenge.
Short Description: Ben feels compelled to take care of the son of a man he killed.

Title: The Ape
Description: In Virginia City Hoss befriends a strong but dimwitted man called Arnie who can’t control his temper. Hoss gets him a job at the Ponderosa.
Short Description: Hoss befriends a strong but dimwitted man who can’t control his temper.

Title: The Avenger
Description: Ben and Adam are accused and found guilty of murder and await their hanging. Joe and Hoss try to get a stay of execution.
Short Description: Ben and Adam are accused and found guilty of murder.
